title: r/Choosingbeggars Seeking New iPhone, New TV... YOU Must Pay!
description:
r/Choosingbeggars The logic of today's choosing beggar is pretty straightforward: They want a new phone and new tv; therefore, some stranger should feel obligated to buy it for them... AND deliver it to their house. As you might expect, the choosing beggar gets some pretty ridiculous responses from people in the comments! If you like this video and want to see more, hit the subscribe button!

Watch on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4GexI8xzFWc
